high_descs: Walk to the fridge then take a step to your left to face the toaster.
Open the cabinet under the counter to the left of the fridge and grab the mug that's down there and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink then turn right to face it.
Wash the mug in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Walk back over to the toaster.
Put the mug in it's place under the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: walk to face cabinet under coffee maker
wash and remove mug from sink
anns.task_desc: put washed mug inside coffee maker

high_descs: Walk over to the section of counter with the toaster and coffee maker on it.
Open the lower right cabinet below the counter and take out the white coffee mug, then close the cabinet.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Wash the mug in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn right and walk over to where the coffee maker is on the counter.
Put the clean white mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean white mug in the coffee maker.
